      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Upon the ledges there was a base above — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This is very obscurely expressed; hut probably by the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "base above ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "is meant the uppermost part of the base; which, though it was above, yet was a base to the laver, which stood upon it. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Certain additions —",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Either as bases for the feet of the said lions and oxen, or only as further ornaments.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
